  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > PLUNGE INTO THE OCEAN OF DARKNESS </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Third-person non-VR </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613850/extras/a0fc9ff1f5ce7d894f4aed6dbeeedada.poster.avif?t=1512314816\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613850/extras/a0fc9ff1f5ce7d894f4aed6dbeeedada.webm?t=1512314816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613850/extras/a0fc9ff1f5ce7d894f4aed6dbeeedada.mp4?t=1512314816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > VR </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613850/extras/ad3784ed3c95aeb38225ee51382bacf4.poster.avif?t=1512314816\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613850/extras/ad3784ed3c95aeb38225ee51382bacf4.webm?t=1512314816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613850/extras/ad3784ed3c95aeb38225ee51382bacf4.mp4?t=1512314816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Radiant Crusade is a stylized fusion between exhilarating car combat and high intensity tower defense action.<br><br>Survive the onslaught of creatures fighting to expel you from the realm of darkness by taking control of a versatile vehicle giving you unshackled locomotion and a powerful arsenal of upgradable abilities.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613850/extras/afeb595b6ea96f1a3d4aeb98060a3bcd.webp?t=1512314816\" width=30 height=30 /></span> Travel at time warping speeds and annihilate enemies in a single blow using the Charge.<br>Leverage the Charge's 'Hyper Time' effect to move through time faster than enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613850/extras/b04c91c8c011e0726ac4200451778daa.webp?t=1512314816\" width=30 height=30 /></span> Utilize tracking Missiles to slow and blast enemies into oblivion.<br>Upgrade missiles with the ability to slow time for each enemy hit!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613850/extras/87257e3da75901d2b34484a83f5cd3b5.webp?t=1512314816\" width=30 height=30 /></span> Deploy Time Bubbles to draw enemies into a time void, in which they seize to a halt upon entry, while taking damage over time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613850/extras/42fa70c61d7d7e1a2eda2e58df7378af.webp?t=1512314816\" width=30 height=30 /></span> Knock back enemies with a powerful AOE blast using the Shotgun<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to play!?</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>In VR, the game is played in the first person perspective, from a cockpit inside the car. <br></li><li>In Non-VR, the game is played from the third-person perspective, behind the car, with full orbit camera controls.<br></li><li>The player drives across a sandbox sized world to combat enemies coming from often distant places, each moving to the center, where the tower is located, and defending itself from.<br></li><li>After each level, expend the increasing amounts of energy to unlock powerful upgrades, using a vast skill tree.<br></li><li>Survive through as many levels as possible, fighting increasingly powerful and varied enemies.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613850/extras/33c9628f53495071d29414c20f612fde.poster.avif?t=1512314816\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613850/extras/33c9628f53495071d29414c20f612fde.webm?t=1512314816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613850/extras/33c9628f53495071d29414c20f612fde.mp4?t=1512314816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
